    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition car that presents nicely overall and should make a very solid driver. The body and paint show well with only typical light cosmetic wear for its age, and the interior is clean and usable without being showroom-perfect. It appears to have been cared for, offering a nice balance of condition, drivability, and value for someone who wants a car they can enjoy without worrying about every little flaw.",
