      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical budget-friendly option for a buyer who wants basic transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with an older used vehicle, but it still offers solid value as an inexpensive daily driver, backup car, or starter vehicle. Priced to sell, it\u2019s a chance to get on the road for less.",
