      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid drivetrain fundamentals and plenty of life left for the next owner. It shows its age cosmetically and will want some TLC, but the engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and it remains a dependable budget-friendly driver. Good candidate for a commuter, first car, or light project if you appreciate straightforward mechanicals and easy ownership. Priced to move and well worth a look for someone who values function over flash.",
      "price": 5900.0,
