      "description": "A car with honest character and plenty of story left to write, this ride is perfect for someone who appreciates personality over polish. It has the kind of presence that makes every errand feel a little more memorable, with a well-lived-in charm and the sort of potential that invites you to make it your own. Whether you need a budget-friendly daily, a hands-on project, or just dependable wheels with soul, this one offers a rare chance to get into something full of possibility without stretching your wallet.",
